strings: <voice_0x0100111E><se_def>*: Bronze is well made. Finally they found you!
<voice_0x0100111F><se_def>*: Carey has spoken out on several occasions.
<voice_0x01001120><se_def>*: I'm sorry I couldn't be with you...
<voice_0x01001121><se_high>*: You're finally here, Cash! But I'm afraid it's already too late.
<voice_0x01001122><se_high>*: Carrie will be with me always.
<voice_0x0100112E><se_high>*: If I were you I'd leave without wasting time.
<voice_0x01001124><se_def>*: Hmm... I didn't know that demons were so powerful here.
<voice_0x01001125><se_def>*: Carrie came and left me when I had a lot of troubles. He was at great risk.
<voice_0x01001126><se_def>*: If you look at something and find something is not right, skip this step. Never mind the monster...
<voice_0x01001127><se_def>rice: It could just be a scam. Add sleeping pills to your diet.
<voice_0x01001128><se_def>rice: But I don't think it will hurt anyone much. He must be tired...
<voice_0x01001129><se_def>*: Yes, I finally made it!
<voice_0x0100112A><se_def>*: But the money was planned.
<voice_0x0100112B><se_def>*: I'm afraid I can't be with you...
<voice_0x0100112C><se_high>*: Then there's the curry! even if it is very late
<voice_0x0100112D><se_high>*: I have been collecting money here for a long time.
<voice_0x0100112E><se_high>*: If I were you I'd leave without wasting time.
<voice_0x01001124><se_def>*: Hmm... I didn't know that demons were so powerful here.
<voice_0x0100112F><se_def>*: When they hit me, Cash came and left me, I was too much in danger...
<voice_0x01001130><se_def>*: If you find him and he is unable to complete his mission, don't let the demons harm him...
<voice_0x01001131><se_high>breathe!: I don't know, but after taking the sleeping pills
<voice_0x01001132><se_high>breathe!: Of course, the victim be damned! Price is very expensive.
